snippet.title: In the world Unknown - Gmtk game jam 2021 || Nastro Studios
snippet.description:
Game Link:-  https://nastrostudios.itch.io/intheworldunknown


In the world Unknown, is an adventure game created by Nastro Studio, for GMTK game jam 2021.

This is a highly atmospheric story adventure game in which, the player is in a very strange dream world and is trapped with an unknown form of light, Now their adventure beings to find out who they really are.....

The ball and the player are connected with an unknown force and their destiny is tied together.......

Main key features of the game:-
* 3d sound (Headphones highly recommended)
* Unique atmospheric look
* Dynamic lighting

Presented by Nastro Studios.

Created by Sagar Chauhan.

About us:-
Nastro Studios is an independent video game development studio, founded in 2019 by Sagar Chauhan.

The goal of Nastro Studio is to create games and experiences that are beautiful and fun to play and to provide its players with the best we can offer.

Our journey started with a dream, a dream to create, a dream to learn, a dream to grow, a dream to provide, a dream to make a difference and we the team here at Nastro Studios will do our best to create them.
